<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="repeat-v">repeat <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'piːt/    美 /rɪ'piːt/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重复；(数字等) 重复出现：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>repeat the same mistake 
犯同样的错误</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will you repeat what you said just now? 
把你刚才说的再重复一遍好吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>repeated /rɪ'piːtɪd/ adj <br />
repeatedly /rɪ'piːtɪdli/ adv <br />
repetition /ˌrepə'tɪʃn/ n   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The teacher asked one student to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (重复) what he had heard from the tape recorder.   （2015 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. repeat  </p></div>